---
title: Pho-Style Beef Noodle Soup with Mushrooms, Bok Choy, Cilantro, Lime & Sriracha
description: Our riff on this iconic Vietnamese noodle soup—with its beefy flavor and aromatics simmered all day—comes together in minutes instead of hours. It boasts earthy mushrooms, chewy ramen noodles, and a one-two crunch punch of napa cabbage and bok choy. Juicy slices of bavette steak top the garlic, ginger, and scallion-infused broth. Finished with herbaceous cilantro, a bright squeeze of lime, and a drizzle of spicy Sriracha, this big bowl is as warming as it is delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pho-style-beef-noodle-soup-f314a261.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pho-style-beef-noodle-soup-63e271349321cb88550e81c4-8cbdb73a.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pho-style-beef-noodle-soup-63e271349321cb88550e81c4
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: Asian
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
  fat: 25 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 100 g
  sugar: 21 g
